# Enforce LF line endings for all text files.
# * text=auto lets Git detect text vs binary; eol=lf forces LF on checkout.
# Required because supabase db diff compares function bodies byte-for-byte,
# and Claude Code has a known bug with CRLF files causing silent corruption.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch line endings
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.otf binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.tar binary
